  I found [this](http://zshwiki.org/home/examples/zlewidgets) via [SU](https://superuser.com/questions/151803/how-do-i-customize-zshs-vim-mode). Here's the basic example, though I'm still customizing it for myself:
  
  ```bash
  function zle-line-init zle-keymap-select {
      RPS1="${${KEYMAP/vicmd/-- NORMAL --}/(main|viins)/-- INSERT --}"
      RPS2=$RPS1
      zle reset-prompt
  }
  
  zle -N zle-line-init
  zle -N zle-keymap-select
  ```
  
