I'm looking for a way to display vi visual and replace mode ...
  URL: https://www.reddit.com/r/zsh/comments/krwm0t/im_looking_for_a_way_to_display_vi_visual_and/
  I'm looking for a way to display vi visual and replace mode in my prompt -- I got insert and command. Help.
